|               |                         ProjectionExec: expr=[l_extendedprice@1 as l_extendedprice, l_discount@2 as l_discount, s_nationkey@0 as s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
